20:31.864 --> 20:35.132
That is a raccoon.
That's a big 'un, yeah.

20:35.134 --> 20:36.934
- Listen, that's okay.
- I'm sorry. Let me go back.

20:36.936 --> 20:39.436
That's okay.
Yeah, he's going back.

20:39.438 --> 20:41.470
- Believe me,
he's meaner. - Okay.

20:47.298 --> 20:48.255
I can't get out.

